sent to pathology.  A coil clip was placed at the site of the biopsy.\nThe wounds were cleaned and dressed.  The patient tolerated the procedure well, and there were no complications.\nPost procedure mammogram of the left breast demonstrated adequate clip placement.\nIMPRESSION:\nUncomplicated ultrasound guided core biopsies of the left breast at the 2 o’clock position and abnormal left axillary lymph node.\n\n","mentions":[{"begin":1820,"end":1824,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_214","classUri":"Left","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":60},{"begin":562,"end":566,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_152","classUri":"Left","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":60},{"begin":1876,"end":1895,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_217","classUri":"AxillaryLymphNode","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":100},{"begin":710,"end":716,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_167","classUri":"Breast","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":90},{"begin":1279,"end":1284,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_192","classUri":"Lymph","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":1710,"end":1716,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_207","classUri":"Breast","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":90},{"begin":414,"end":418,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_140","classUri":"Left","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":60},{"begin":1885,"end":1890,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_219","classUri":"Lymph","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":644,"end":652,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_160","classUri":"Axilla","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":100},{"begin":1270,"end":1278,"id":"fake_patient2_07072025191759_M_191","classUri":"Axilla","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":100},{"begin":419,"end":425,"i